    <!-- Onboarding — Guide -->
    <string name="guide_skip">Skip</string>
    <string name="guide_next">Next</string>
    <string name="guide_finish">Get Started</string>
    <string name="guide_title_1">Welcome to AetherX</string>
    <string name="guide_body_1">Optimize your phone\'s touch response before playing Free Fire. Adjust DPI, resolution, pointer speed, and refresh rate all in one place.</string>
    <string name="guide_title_2">Why Does the Screen Feel \'Smoother\'?</string>
    <string name="guide_body_2">Lowering DPI and resolution makes touch-to-pixel mapping more precise, while a higher refresh rate makes movement feel smoother and more responsive.</string>
    <string name="guide_title_3">Safe &amp; Reversible</string>
    <string name="guide_body_3">All changes use official Android system commands (wm, settings) and can be reset to factory defaults anytime with the Reset button.</string>
    <string name="guide_title_4">Ready to Tweak</string>
    <string name="guide_body_4">Open the Tweak tab, then drag a slider or flip a switch as you like. Changes apply instantly to the system without pressing anything else, even while playing Free Fire.</string>

